# REST Client requests (VS Code "humao.rest-client").
# Start the stack first: `make up && make run`.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@secret = dev-secret-change-me

### Health check -> {"status": "ok"}
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/

### Create an order -> 201
# @name createOrder
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Ada Lovelace",
  "total_amount": "42.50"
}

### Create an order with an invalid amount -> 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_name": "Bad Order",
  "total_amount": "-5"
}

### List all orders (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/

### List orders filtered by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/?status=synced

### Retrieve the order created above
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{createOrder.response.body.id}}/

### Partner webhook — valid secret -> 202
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/partner/
Content-Type: application/json
X-Partner-Secret: {{secret}}

{
  "event": "order.updated",
  "id": "123"
}

### Partner webhook — bad secret -> 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/partner/
Content-Type: application/json
X-Partner-Secret: wrong

{
  "event": "order.updated",
  "id": "123"
}
